    <item>
      <title>拼多多 550 亿美元股价暴跌给中国经济敲响警钟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/china-s-crashing-consumer-star-sounds-alarm-on-economic-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国消费仅存的亮点之一正在迅速消退，因为该国的经济低迷甚至对最容易获得商品的需求也产生了影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/china-s-crashing-consumer-star-sounds-alarm-on-economic-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 04:12:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚对社交媒体许可计划的阻力不以为然</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/malaysia-plan-to-license-social-media-platforms-sparks-pushback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚将按计划推进其对消息和社交媒体服务提供商的监管计划，而不受业界要求政府暂时搁置此举以进一步考虑的呼声影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/malaysia-plan-to-license-social-media-platforms-sparks-pushback</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 01:59:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>扎克伯格称白宫“施压”Meta 删除与新冠疫情相关的帖子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/meta-ceo-says-he-was-pressured-by-biden-to-pull-covid-content</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 首席执行官马克·扎克伯格声称，在全球疫情期间，Facebook 受到美国政府的“压力”，要求其审查与新冠肺炎相关的内容，他对公司接受这些要求的决定感到遗憾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/meta-ceo-says-he-was-pressured-by-biden-to-pull-covid-content</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 01:52:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拼多多的警告凸显中国消费品企业面临的压力日益加大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/pdd-s-warning-highlights-growing-strain-on-china-consumer-firms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拼多多控股有限公司警告称，随着竞争持续升温，其收入增长将放缓，中国消费企业的前景看起来愈发黯淡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/pdd-s-warning-highlights-growing-strain-on-china-consumer-firms</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 01:52:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>LG 电子考虑在印度上市，以达到 750 亿美元的目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/lg-electronics-weighs-india-ipo-to-help-chase-75-billion-goal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[LG 电子公司正在考虑为其印度业务进行首次公开​​募股，利用蓬勃发展的股票市场，帮助其到 2030 年实现 750 亿美元的电子产品收入的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/lg-electronics-weighs-india-ipo-to-help-chase-75-billion-goal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Telegram 亿万富翁的叛逆性格使他的自由受到威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/telegram-founder-pavel-durov-net-worth-detention-in-france-puts-freedom-at-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[帕维尔·杜罗夫对监管的自由放任态度使即时通讯应用 Telegram 成为巨头，也为他提供了一个从迪拜之巅与从莫斯科到布鲁塞尔的官员发生冲突的平台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/telegram-founder-pavel-durov-net-worth-detention-in-france-puts-freedom-at-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 18:42:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
